::Feline::

She stayed at Zardus' side.  She looked at Skulletron.  She let out a 
loud meow with a low growl.  She stepped closer to Zardus and rubber 
her shoulder against him.  She moved her head under his hand and 
purred.



--- In nbwrpg@egroups.com, Yanshosh@a... wrote:
> ::Zardus/Bloodystrike::
> 
> Bloodystrike runs off after Skulletron, heading for the mess hall.
> ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
> Zardus's hand slides down to Feline's side, petting lightly. He 
turns his 
> head as Bloodystrike walks in.
> 
> "Zardus, this is Skulletron," Bloodystrike says, pointing to 
Skulletron, 
> "Skulletron, this is Zardus."
> 
> Zardus stands up, keeping his hand on Feline and looking at 
Skulletron. 
> "Welcome to the Alliance, Skulletron. I assume Bloodystrike gave 
you a tour?"
